  <prompt>Implement the top-level orchestration that combines FieldDiscovery + IdentityNormalization + OrganizationMembership + per-user Redis cache (5-min TTL) and builds FetchXML to query the target entity for matching rows.</prompt>
  <goal>MembershipResolverService.ResolveAsync(systemUserId, entityType, options) returns MembershipResponse with ids[], byRole map, identity, count. Per-user cache 5-min TTL (Phase 1A; Phase 2 lengthens TTL with pub/sub invalidation).</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec FR-1A.8">Per-user cache 5-min TTL (Phase 1A); no write invalidation</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-009">Redis</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-016">Cache + retry pattern</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md §A">BFF pre-merge checklist</constraint>
  </constraints>
  <knowledge>
    <topic>membership-orchestration</topic>
    <files>
      <file>docs/adr/ADR-009-redis-caching.md</file>
      <file>docs/adr/ADR-013-ai-architecture.md</file>
      <file>docs/adr/ADR-016-rate-limits.md</file>
      <file>.claude/patterns/dataverse/web-api-client.md</file>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Nodes/QueryDataverseNodeExecutor.cs</file>
      <file>projects/spaarke-platform-foundations-r3/spec.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>
  <steps>
    <step order="0">Context check + FR-1A.5 through FR-1A.8</step>
    <step order="1">Implement IMembershipResolverService.ResolveAsync(systemUserId, entityType, options)</step>
    <step order="2">Pull discovered descriptors (from FieldDiscoveryService)</step>
    <step order="3">Pull PersonIdentity (from IdentityNormalizationService)</step>
    <step order="4">For each descriptor, build FetchXML condition matching the user's identity values</step>
    <step order="5">Combine into single OR-joined FetchXML; execute against target entity</step>
    <step order="6">Group results by role; return MembershipResponse</step>
    <step order="7">Per-user cache 5-min TTL keyed on {systemUserId, entityType, optionsHash}</step>
    <step order="8">Unit tests: orchestration paths; integration test against spaarkedev1 fixture</step>
  </steps>
  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">ResolveAsync returns expected IDs for seeded user (AC-1A.3)</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">byRole map populated correctly</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Cache hit on second call within 5min</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">p95 ≤300ms for ≤500-membership user on 50K-row entity (AC-1A.5; verify via App Insights post-deploy)</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
